---
title: Speedy Peanut Beef Tacos with Crispy Shallots
description: Inspired by our South East Asian neighbours and their fun & fragrant street food - we reckon the whole family is going to go totally nuts for these peanut beef tacos. And if they are peanut butter obsessed like us, just try stopping them from dipping, dunking and smothering their tacos in lots of the nutty goodness!
